The '''Turkish Studies Association''' is [[learned society]] established in 1971 for the promotion of [[Turkish people|Turkish]] and [[Ottoman studies]]. It was previously known as the '''Turkish Studies Group'''. It publishes the ''[[Turkish Studies Association Journal]]'' (formerly ''Turkish Studies Association Bulletin'').
